description:
Summer is here and Older Nep is ready to take in the sunshine with the SWIMSUIT COSTUME SET! The Swimsuit Costume Set includes 12x swimsuit outfits for each playable character*:
*Older Neptune
*Neptune
*Pippih
*Jagaa
*Reedio
*Noire
*Blanc
*Vert
*Nepgear
*Uni
*Rom
*Ram
name: Swimsuit Costume Set
